{"date":"2001-12-15","platform":"剧场版","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/4c/cf/47144_402XA.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/4c/cf/47144_402XA.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/4c/cf/47144_402XA.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/4c/cf/47144_402XA.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/4c/cf/47144_402XA.jpg"},"summary":"这是关于九龙大角咀猪样小朋友麦兜的成长故事，由他的出生、上幼儿园、上中学、再讲讲讲讲，到负家产的故事。麦兜单纯乐观、资质平平，却有很多梦想。麦太是单亲妈妈，把所有梦想寄托在儿子身上。希望、失望、希望、失望……一个一个的，都是失败，但麦兜还是凭着他正直善良的「死蠢」，创造了他美丽的世界。出生时出现异象的麦兜，在妈妈心目中总希望他与众不同。香港得了第一面奥运金牌，妈妈于是带著麦兜找到了教练，希望麦兜也能为国争光。日子一天天过去，麦兜也长大了，虽然未能夺得金牌光耀乡里，但是他还是麦兜，独一无二的麦兜。","name":"麥兜故事","name_cn":"麦兜故事","tags":[{"name":"国产","count":198,"total_cont":0},{"name":"剧场版","count":170,"total_cont":0},{"name":"童年","count":138,"total_cont":0},{"name":"治愈","count":120,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2001","count":102,"total_cont":0},{"name":"香港","count":88,"total_cont":0},{"name":"麦兜","count":63,"total_cont":0},{"name":"搞笑","count":52,"total_cont":0},{"name":"原创","count":49,"total_cont":0},{"name":"动画电影","count":48,"total_cont":0},{"name":"电影","count":21,"total_cont":0},{"name":"TVB","count":21,"total_cont":0},{"name":"映画","count":13,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2001年","count":12,"total_cont":0},{"name":"治愈系","count":10,"total_cont":0},{"name":"中国","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"谢立文","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日常","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2000s","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"漫画改","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"动画","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"中国动画","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"袁建滔","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"00年代","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"劇場版","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"謝立文","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"补标","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"神作","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"国产动画","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"反复","count":2,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key":"中文名","value":"麦兜故事"},{"key":"别名","value":[{"v":"My Life as McDull"}]},